CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1963, pg. 4, reads: "It's Cold Outside! - But when Pat Stevens, demure model, wore this Simonetta Italian knit sweater over colorful slacks, the audience grew warmer. She was one of the five D. I. models. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Pat Stevens wearing diagonal patterned pants and light colored diamond patterned turtleneck sweater with fringe at neckline, standing in Holiday House for annual D. I. Club MENDS benefit
